description:
The paint is dry, which means assembly of the Buick 401 Nailhead can finally begin. It’ll be easy—just put it back together, right? Not so fast—there’s a proper way to assemble a set of Buick cylinder heads. Davin’s first challenge, however: is the paint color blue or green?
